    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "ok i get the tension part. what about the internal stuff though? like, if you were looking inside a finished slab, is there anything else happening in there besides the rebar and the concrete itself? just wondering if there are other factors or things that change the integrity of the mix once it's set.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
